               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I went to unscrew the bolts, and saw the till partly open; I went to shut it, and Mr. Smith accused me of robbing it; I saw my master get up from under the counter.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SMITH</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. I was there watching him—there are no bolts behind the counter.</p>
